Atlanta.title: Atlanta
Atlanta.plot: Two cousins, with different views on art versus commerce, on their way up through the Atlanta rap scene; Earnest 'Earn' Marks, an ambitious college dropout and his estranged cousin, who suddenly becomes a star.

Mr.Robot.title: Mr.Robot
Mr.Robot.plot: A contemporary and culturally resonant drama about a young programmer, Elliot, who suffers from a debilitating anti-social disorder and decides that he can only connect to people by hacking them. He wields his skills as a weapon to protect the people that he cares about. Elliot will find himself in the intersection between a cybersecurity firm he works for and the underworld organizations that are recruiting him to bring down corporate America.

Luke_Cage.title: Luke Cage
Luke_Cage.plot: Given superstrength and durability by a sabotaged experiment, a wrongly accused man escapes prison to become a superhero for hire.

Alterned Carbon.title: Alterned Carbon
Alterned Carbon.plot: After 250 years on ice, a prisoner returns to life in a new body with one chance to win his freedom: by solving a mind-bending murder.

The_walking_Dead.title: The Walking Dead
The_walking_Dead.plot: Sheriff's deputy Rick Grimes awakens from a coma to find a post-apocalyptic world dominated by flesh-eating zombies. He sets out to find his family and encounters many other survivors along the way.

BoJack Horseman.title: BoJack Horseman
BoJack Horseman.plot: Meet the most beloved sitcom horse of the 90s - 20 years later. BoJack Horseman was the star of the hit TV show 'Horsin' Around,' but today he's washed up, living in Hollywood, complaining about everything, and wearing colorful sweaters.

11_22_63.plot: An English teacher travels back in time to prevent the Kennedy assassination, but discovers he is attached to the life he has made in a bygone era.

black_mirror.title: Black Mirror
black_mirror.plot: An anthology series exploring a twisted, high-tech multiverse where humanity's greatest innovations and darkest instincts collide.

blue_mountain_state.title: Blue Mountain State
blue_mountain_state.plot: Three incoming freshmen attending Midwestern college football powerhouse Blue Mountain State must quickly adapt to college life and juggle football, girls, classes and nonstop hazing

brooklyn_nine_nine.title: Brooklyn Nine Nine
brooklyn_nine_nine.plot: "Brooklyn Nine-Nine" follows the exploits of hilarious Det. Jake Peralta and his diverse, lovable colleagues as they police the NYPD's 99th Precinct

Game_of_Thrones.title: Game of Thrones
Game_of_Thrones.plot: Nine noble families fight for control over the lands of Westeros, while an ancient enemy returns after being dormant for millennia.

Sex_Education.title: Sex Education
Sex_Education.plot: Inexperienced Otis channels his sex therapist mom when he teams up with rebellious Maeve to set up an underground sex therapy clinic at school.

Prison Break - Complete.title: Prison Break
Prison Break - Complete.plot: Due to a political conspiracy, an innocent man is sent to death row and his only hope is his brother, who makes it his mission to deliberately get himself sent to the same prison in order to break the both of them out, from the inside

Sarah_Connor_Chronicles.title: Terminator: The Sarah Connor Chronicles
Sarah_Connor_Chronicles.plot: Set after the events in Terminator 2: Judgment Day (1991), Sarah Connor and her son, John, try to stay under-the-radar from the government, as they plot to destroy the computer network, Skynet, in hopes of preventing Armageddon

Silicon_Valley.title: Silicon_Valley
Silicon_Valley.plot: Follows the struggle of Richard Hendricks, a Silicon Valley engineer trying to build his own company called Pied Piper

the_last_man_on_earth.title: The last man on earth
the_last_man_on_earth.plot: A cancer researcher finds herself in over her head after following her mentor to a corporate biotech
